# Security Tooling Account
# 
# This account houses centralized security monitoring and incident response tools:
# - AWS Security Hub (delegated administrator)
# - Amazon GuardDuty (threat detection)
# - AWS Config (compliance monitoring)
# - Amazon Inspector (vulnerability assessment)
# - IAM Access Analyzer (external access detection)
# - AWS Audit Manager (compliance automation)
# - Amazon Detective (security investigation)
# - AWS Firewall Manager (centralized firewall policies)
#
# Following AWS best practices from:
# https://docs.aws.amazon.com/whitepapers/latest/organizing-your-aws-environment/foundational-ous.html#security-ou
#
